children.text: Step forward with a leg and bend it until both legs are in a 90 degree angle.
Make sure your body stays in a straight line on top of your rear knee.
Push through your front heel to activate your glutes and get back to the starting position.
Engage your core as you twist your torso.
As one hand is supporting your body move the other straight above your head.
Keep both arms in line with each other and your shoulders.
Make it easier by placing your knees on the ground.
